K8S COMMANDS:
USED FOR :
Deploying applications to Kubernetes
Monitoring pods and services
Debugging issues

kubectl version
kubectl get nodes

kubectl create namespace smartshop
kubectl get ns

kubectl apply -f k8s/
kubectl get pods -n smartshop
kubectl get svc -n smartshop

kubectl describe pod <pod-name> -n smartshop
kubectl logs <pod-name> -n smartshop
